videos.description: Purdue's Trevion Williams sneaks his way inside and snags a pass from Carsen Edwards to slam it home.
videos.headline: Williams sneaks past defender for massive dunk

videos.description: Grady Eifert drops a long-range three to set a career high in points to put the Boilermakers up 47-35.
videos.headline: Eifert records career high for Boilers with deep 3
